WEBVTT

00:11.430 --> 00:16.660
[2012] [After the 8.17 Case]

00:54.110 --> 00:54.520
Good.

00:57.480 --> 00:58.310
Lang,

00:58.340 --> 00:59.300
you're back.

01:03.040 --> 01:04.170
Are you hungry, Son?

01:04.680 --> 01:06.430
Are you hungry? Are you hungry?

01:06.760 --> 01:07.400
Are you?

01:09.510 --> 01:10.110
Wait here.

01:11.150 --> 01:12.310
I'll cook for you.

01:16.150 --> 01:16.640
Dad!

01:21.150 --> 01:21.760
What is it?

01:38.479 --> 01:39.680
Qi Yan is also hungry.

01:48.060 --> 01:48.620
Dad.

01:52.200 --> 01:53.060
I'm hungry too.

01:57.580 --> 01:58.580
Where is Wen Lang?

01:59.370 --> 02:00.780
Where is my son Wen Lang?

02:06.680 --> 02:07.350
Where is he?

02:08.190 --> 02:09.520
Where is my son Wen Lang?

02:12.120 --> 02:12.780
Where is he?

02:13.310 --> 02:14.360
Where is Wen Lang?

02:14.400 --> 02:15.730
Say something! Tell me!

02:15.810 --> 02:16.540
Where is Wen Lang?

02:16.540 --> 02:17.430
Tell me!

02:22.770 --> 02:24.360
He died.

02:28.360 --> 02:29.630
He died?

02:31.240 --> 02:33.150
He was shot dead by the police

02:36.710 --> 02:38.590
when he tried to protect me.

02:41.470 --> 02:42.600
One shot to the head.

02:43.780 --> 02:45.040
He got shot in the head,

02:47.800 --> 02:48.560
and died.

02:53.480 --> 02:55.410
But your other son is still around.

02:56.270 --> 02:57.540
I, Qi Yan, am with you.

03:06.650 --> 03:08.110
I'll take good care of you.

03:17.790 --> 03:18.920
How did Wen Lang die?

03:20.310 --> 03:21.680
Did you kill him?

05:06.090 --> 05:11.780
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

05:12.100 --> 05:14.420
[Episode 27]

05:27.550 --> 05:28.310
Qi Yan.

05:35.560 --> 05:36.560
Professor Jiang,

05:37.270 --> 05:38.930
you are always sharp as a tack.

05:40.000 --> 05:41.200
Are you done playing?

05:41.720 --> 05:42.650
Unfortunately,

05:43.630 --> 05:45.159
since you were distracted,

05:46.310 --> 05:47.390
the game already ended

05:47.390 --> 05:48.720
before it even started.

05:50.020 --> 05:51.360
Your sharpness could save

05:51.360 --> 05:52.800
an entire SWAT team,

05:53.159 --> 05:55.810
but not the girl you love dearly.

06:01.050 --> 06:02.250
The game won't be over

06:02.900 --> 06:04.500
in 51 minutes and 48 seconds.

06:05.950 --> 06:06.680
Impressive.

06:07.270 --> 06:08.270
Professor Jiang,

06:09.160 --> 06:11.410
you must've found the tip
I left at your home.

06:11.410 --> 06:13.420
[Jiang Hansheng]

06:31.800 --> 06:33.260
You are still in Jingzhou.

06:34.390 --> 06:36.450
Is this your guess, Professor Jiang?

06:37.100 --> 06:37.890
Try harder.

06:38.830 --> 06:41.830
You are basically throwing away
Officer Zhou's life.

06:44.750 --> 06:45.610
Are you in town,

06:47.710 --> 06:48.740
or the suburbs?

06:56.840 --> 06:58.370
The suburbs then, I assume.

06:59.560 --> 07:00.240
Qi Yan,

07:01.270 --> 07:03.160
you enjoy seeking attention,

07:03.680 --> 07:05.070
but to make sure the game

07:05.070 --> 07:06.600
can go on smoothly,

07:07.060 --> 07:08.810
I bet you would choose a quiet

07:09.110 --> 07:10.310
and remote location.

07:14.560 --> 07:15.690
I don't understand.

07:16.040 --> 07:18.230
[Search Results of Properties
Registered to Wen Lang]

07:16.720 --> 07:18.980
What do you mean
by "seeking attention"?

07:21.480 --> 07:23.540
When children are too young to speak,

07:24.510 --> 07:25.630
they usually

07:26.190 --> 07:26.800
make noise

07:27.390 --> 07:27.990
by crying,

07:28.800 --> 07:31.530
screaming, and throwing things,
so as to attract

07:31.560 --> 07:33.290
their caregivers' attention.

07:35.159 --> 07:35.750
Qi Yan,

07:36.950 --> 07:39.680
you specifically
targeted women in red dresses.

07:41.070 --> 07:43.530
Whose attention
were you trying to attract?

07:52.890 --> 07:53.450
Alright.

07:54.950 --> 07:56.750
Let's set aside the past for now.

07:57.280 --> 07:59.250
Everything you're doing now only serves

07:59.250 --> 08:00.790
the purpose of getting back at me

08:00.790 --> 08:02.050
and avenging Wen Lang.

08:05.510 --> 08:07.240
If I were you,

08:08.070 --> 08:09.070
I would choose a place

08:09.070 --> 08:10.830
where Wen Lang could see.

08:18.750 --> 08:19.880
My guess is correct.

08:23.940 --> 08:24.690
Perhaps...

08:26.720 --> 08:28.720
you're at where Wen Lang was buried?

08:33.730 --> 08:34.590
No, it's wrong.

08:36.590 --> 08:38.190
Then you must be in his house.

08:44.700 --> 08:46.560
Looks like I've guessed it right.

08:47.320 --> 08:48.850
You're in Wen Lang's house.

09:07.200 --> 09:08.200
Professor Jiang,

09:08.720 --> 09:09.980
you are truly amazing.

09:10.500 --> 09:12.100
Really, if there is a chance,

09:12.670 --> 09:14.360
I would love to ask you

09:14.360 --> 09:16.220
about your tricks for reasoning.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.390
Will you teach me?

09:18.030 --> 09:19.630
Let me hear Zhou Jin's voice.

09:19.800 --> 09:20.920
Then I'll tell you

09:21.440 --> 09:22.860
what gave your secrets away.

09:22.860 --> 09:25.190
How are you so sure
that she's still alive?

09:27.750 --> 09:28.680
Jiang Hansheng,

09:29.710 --> 09:32.280
there isn't much time left for you.

09:36.940 --> 09:38.670
A property in the southern suburbs

09:38.670 --> 09:40.080
belonged to Wen Lang.

09:40.300 --> 09:42.320
I found the exact location
of Qi Yan's phone—

09:42.320 --> 09:44.380
Zongsen Beach in Chengnan District.

09:52.120 --> 09:52.920
What is it now?

09:53.120 --> 09:54.850
Has something happened again?

09:55.080 --> 09:56.960
Everything is fine. Don't worry.

09:57.130 --> 09:58.060
I'm here for you.

10:12.590 --> 10:14.360
Come on, let's record this—

10:14.380 --> 10:16.500
the cheerful Officer Jiang.

10:18.480 --> 10:19.880
How is it, Officer Jiang?

10:20.510 --> 10:21.770
Are you feeling great?

10:23.110 --> 10:25.230
As we told you, this is good stuff.

10:25.250 --> 10:26.760
We'd never lie to you.

10:38.870 --> 10:39.960
So beautiful.

10:42.060 --> 10:43.260
What did you just say?

10:44.600 --> 10:45.600
The sunset glow.

10:47.910 --> 10:49.510
It's so beautiful.

11:29.720 --> 11:30.910
The sunset glow

11:38.390 --> 11:40.080
is so beautiful.

11:44.260 --> 11:45.320
The sunset glow...

11:50.550 --> 11:52.440
What sunset glow could be

11:54.840 --> 11:55.910
so beautiful

11:58.390 --> 11:59.870
that you can't forget?

12:03.240 --> 12:04.200
I hate you.

12:07.640 --> 12:09.190
You've never taken me to see

12:11.360 --> 12:13.270
such beautiful sunset glow.

12:15.060 --> 12:16.460
Is that any way to behave?

12:30.390 --> 12:31.240
Hansheng,

12:33.390 --> 12:35.080
look how foolish he is,

12:36.490 --> 12:38.150
for making me dress like this.

13:14.250 --> 13:16.380
How did they get to know about Wen Lang?

13:17.320 --> 13:20.500
Their judgement has never failed again
during all this time.

13:20.500 --> 13:22.980
Isn't it too risky to lure Jiang Hansheng

13:24.060 --> 13:25.780
to this place?

13:28.390 --> 13:29.200
It's Qi Zhen.

13:30.730 --> 13:32.810
Qi Zhen has been with the police.

13:34.200 --> 13:34.830
Young Master Wen...

13:34.830 --> 13:35.470
"Yan."

13:47.190 --> 13:49.460
Call me "Yan."

13:50.430 --> 13:51.150
Yan...

13:52.400 --> 13:54.260
You didn't fear Young Master Wen.

13:55.650 --> 13:57.770
Why are you afraid of Yan?

13:59.960 --> 14:01.170
I just feel...

14:02.210 --> 14:03.610
you're a bit unfamiliar.

14:09.300 --> 14:10.230
You are right.

14:13.120 --> 14:14.320
What did you just say?

14:15.660 --> 14:17.180
I was trying to say

14:19.030 --> 14:21.200
things are not looking up for us.

14:21.630 --> 14:23.270
We're out of helpers.

14:23.790 --> 14:24.320
Well,

14:25.130 --> 14:27.460
if they really track us down
to this place,

14:28.270 --> 14:29.720
how are we going to escape?

14:29.720 --> 14:30.920
Why should we escape?

14:34.080 --> 14:34.940
Are you afraid?

14:38.630 --> 14:40.270
If you are, then leave.

14:42.440 --> 14:43.480
Leave alone.

15:15.960 --> 15:16.890
I'm not leaving.

15:23.150 --> 15:24.060
I knew it.

15:25.120 --> 15:27.190
My girl Qiu Ye is a responsible woman.

15:28.200 --> 15:28.840
Right?

15:33.700 --> 15:35.100
This is an important day.

15:36.990 --> 15:38.720
Why are you wearing this dress?

15:40.330 --> 15:41.160
How do you...

15:41.980 --> 15:43.860
have time to even notice me today?

15:56.510 --> 15:58.710
I've been watching you the entire time.

16:01.420 --> 16:02.350
The entire time.

16:07.370 --> 16:08.770
Put on a different dress.

16:10.830 --> 16:13.310
You know what I'd like to see.

16:30.700 --> 16:32.150
Get a move on!

16:56.120 --> 16:57.520
Your husband is useless.

16:58.910 --> 17:01.110
He won't get to see you for one last time.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.800
What's there to laugh at?

17:13.400 --> 17:15.599
Does it matter
if he gets to see me or not?

17:16.270 --> 17:17.530
However useless he is,

17:18.640 --> 17:20.170
he's still better than you.

17:24.440 --> 17:25.200
Is that so?

17:25.400 --> 17:26.109
Qi Yan,

17:27.310 --> 17:28.590
you really...

17:29.960 --> 17:31.560
can't bear to lose to others.

17:32.640 --> 17:34.320
But you have already suffered

17:36.170 --> 17:38.340
a humiliating loss to Jiang Hansheng.

17:39.240 --> 17:40.500
You're jealous of him,

17:40.830 --> 17:42.110
so you wish

17:42.240 --> 17:43.500
he will end up like you,

17:44.070 --> 17:46.680
a pathetic worm rolling in the mud.

17:47.400 --> 17:48.960
You want to drag him down so badly

17:48.960 --> 17:50.550
that you don't mind
resorting to whatever it takes.

17:50.550 --> 17:52.210
But can that get you anywhere?

17:52.480 --> 17:54.440
No matter what you do,

17:56.510 --> 17:58.040
the difference between you

17:59.240 --> 18:01.440
and Jiang Hansheng will always remain.

18:02.550 --> 18:03.610
That's because...

18:05.070 --> 18:07.680
nobody cares about you.

18:08.640 --> 18:10.680
Meanwhile, he is loved

18:11.920 --> 18:13.000
by many.

18:14.640 --> 18:16.480
Even if you drag him down,

18:17.750 --> 18:19.480
I'll be there at the bottom

18:20.670 --> 18:21.600
holding him up.

18:22.920 --> 18:26.510
Indeed, guilt can't cause you misery.

18:28.480 --> 18:30.510
What truly brings you pain

18:32.070 --> 18:34.160
is your inferiority complex.

19:01.000 --> 19:03.110
Officer Zhou!

19:03.960 --> 19:06.310
You hurt me.

19:07.440 --> 19:11.280
And you must pay a price for it!

19:17.030 --> 19:18.900
Officer Zhou,

19:19.270 --> 19:20.750
where are you?

19:24.750 --> 19:26.480
Where are you?

19:30.000 --> 19:32.040
Officer Zhou!

19:54.310 --> 19:56.200
You found a hideout yet?

19:56.510 --> 19:58.640
I'm coming to find you!

20:06.150 --> 20:07.200
Why are you helping me?

20:07.200 --> 20:08.510
There's no way I can leave.

20:08.510 --> 20:10.640
But I hope you can get my son out of here.

20:11.520 --> 20:12.750
Forget about anything else.

20:12.750 --> 20:13.680
Will you promise me

20:13.680 --> 20:14.750
to help my son out of here?

20:14.750 --> 20:15.640
Where is your son?

20:15.640 --> 20:17.030
The first room by the stairway.

20:17.030 --> 20:18.090
On the first floor?

20:18.480 --> 20:19.810
But I don't have the key.

20:20.940 --> 20:22.670
You have to break the door open.

20:24.070 --> 20:25.070
I'm begging you.

20:25.200 --> 20:27.270
Officer Zhou!

20:27.640 --> 20:28.790
Got a hideout yet?

20:28.790 --> 20:29.680
I'll deal with him.

20:29.680 --> 20:31.240
I'm coming to find you.

20:33.240 --> 20:35.550
Officer Zhou, where are you?

20:44.030 --> 20:48.160
Where are you?

21:19.350 --> 21:20.960
I'm about to catch you,

21:21.480 --> 21:23.160
Officer Zhou.

21:27.830 --> 21:29.140
You betrayed me.

21:36.640 --> 21:38.830
You betrayed me!

21:39.940 --> 21:41.140
Stop it.

21:41.510 --> 21:43.400
Stop all this, Young Master Wen.

21:46.160 --> 21:48.830
I am Qi Yan.

21:50.000 --> 21:52.440
I shouldn't have saved you years ago.

21:52.920 --> 21:54.510
I should have let Wen Hongsheng

21:54.510 --> 21:57.350
beat you and your son to death,

21:57.790 --> 21:59.750
and had you bled dry.

22:00.350 --> 22:03.060
This is how you repay my kindness, huh?

22:03.720 --> 22:04.440
I beg you

22:04.630 --> 22:06.190
to spare my son.

22:06.680 --> 22:07.240
I beg you.

22:08.590 --> 22:09.400
Spare him.

22:09.660 --> 22:10.450
Please.

22:10.480 --> 22:11.280
Please.

22:11.830 --> 22:12.640
Please!

22:15.920 --> 22:16.720
Qiu Ye.

22:19.310 --> 22:21.070
Do you know why I would always forgive you

22:21.070 --> 22:22.930
no matter what mistakes you made?

22:24.510 --> 22:25.840
Because you would never

22:27.550 --> 22:28.790
give up on your child

22:28.790 --> 22:30.550
under any circumstances.

22:37.350 --> 22:38.550
You're a good mother.

22:56.560 --> 22:58.490
But this time, I won't forgive you.

23:18.440 --> 23:19.160
Little boy,

23:19.250 --> 23:19.680
come with me.

23:19.680 --> 23:20.370
I want my mom!

23:20.370 --> 23:22.160
I'll take you to your mom now, okay?

23:22.160 --> 23:22.790
Really?

23:22.790 --> 23:23.790
Really. Let's go.

23:42.680 --> 23:43.790
Back off!

23:43.920 --> 23:45.400
Back off now.

23:47.220 --> 23:48.020
Let him go.

23:49.070 --> 23:51.480
Why should I let him go?

24:00.520 --> 24:02.180
Officer Zhou, what are you...

24:03.070 --> 24:04.270
If you kill him,

24:05.830 --> 24:07.900
I will die right in front of you.

24:08.440 --> 24:09.720
Don't you just want to use me

24:09.720 --> 24:11.320
to threaten Jiang Hansheng?

24:11.640 --> 24:12.640
If I'm dead,

24:14.550 --> 24:16.750
what will you have to threaten him with?

24:20.070 --> 24:22.070
You will lose completely.

25:03.160 --> 25:04.820
Report to the command center:

25:04.920 --> 25:07.230
The surveillance team has reached
the outer perimeter of the villa.

25:07.230 --> 25:08.030
Report:

25:08.350 --> 25:10.510
We have visual on the first floor.
It's clear.

25:10.510 --> 25:11.170
Roger that.

25:11.270 --> 25:13.310
Sniper point 2, report in.

25:13.840 --> 25:14.360
Report:

25:14.720 --> 25:16.180
Curtains on the second and third floors
are drawn.

25:16.180 --> 25:17.840
Unable to locate the suspect.

25:18.110 --> 25:18.710
Chief Tan,

25:19.070 --> 25:20.410
since the villa backs onto the sea,

25:20.410 --> 25:21.590
there's no way we can acquire

25:21.590 --> 25:23.440
useful information
on the inside the villa.

25:23.440 --> 25:24.240
Deploy a drone

25:24.440 --> 25:25.640
to observe in the air.

25:25.640 --> 25:26.160
Yes.

25:49.350 --> 25:50.080
I'm here now.

25:51.590 --> 25:53.320
You're late, Professor Jiang.

25:55.130 --> 25:56.130
Where is Zhou Jin?

25:56.590 --> 25:58.440
Would you like to hear her voice?

25:59.750 --> 26:01.510
Go away! Don't touch me!

26:13.840 --> 26:14.900
Are you satisfied?

26:15.850 --> 26:16.570
Qi Yan,

26:17.830 --> 26:19.960
Zhou Jin is your only bargaining chip.

26:20.240 --> 26:21.980
Don't blow your chance to negotiate.

26:21.980 --> 26:23.190
Rest assured. As I said,

26:23.190 --> 26:24.590
the game has just begun.

26:26.240 --> 26:27.500
If we are to negotiate,

26:28.000 --> 26:29.920
a face-to-face meeting is more sincere.

26:29.920 --> 26:31.320
Right, Professor Jiang?

26:32.400 --> 26:33.730
I'll be waiting for you.

26:34.690 --> 26:35.380
By the way,

26:36.110 --> 26:38.110
if you want to bring in someone else,

26:38.540 --> 26:39.820
go ahead and try.

26:40.650 --> 26:44.800
I promise they will be surprised.

26:54.350 --> 26:56.280
The situation inside the building

26:56.920 --> 26:58.450
is completely unclear now.

26:58.720 --> 26:59.590
What is Qi Yan

26:59.790 --> 27:00.790
up to?

27:01.720 --> 27:02.920
Is Zhou Jin safe?

27:04.000 --> 27:05.660
We don't know the answers yet.

27:06.480 --> 27:08.350
There are too many uncertainties.

27:08.350 --> 27:09.610
Rushing into the villa

27:10.310 --> 27:11.570
will put you in danger.

27:12.720 --> 27:15.650
But the danger will multiply
if we keep waiting here.

27:16.270 --> 27:17.680
Qi Yan has been timing me.

27:18.240 --> 27:20.350
I have to get in there
now that I've arrived.

27:20.350 --> 27:20.960
Chief Tan,

27:21.510 --> 27:22.590
he asked to meet me alone.

27:22.590 --> 27:24.320
I'm sure he has his own demands.

27:24.750 --> 27:26.880
He has nothing else to threaten me with.

27:26.880 --> 27:27.880
Without Zhou Jin,

27:28.110 --> 27:29.170
he has no leverage.

27:29.590 --> 27:32.650
"If you want to bring in someone else,
go ahead and try."

27:33.050 --> 27:33.850
I think

27:34.820 --> 27:36.680
we are left with no other options.

27:38.000 --> 27:39.000
Professor Jiang,

27:39.160 --> 27:40.420
after you get in there,

27:40.510 --> 27:41.750
try to quickly confirm

27:41.750 --> 27:42.550
where Zhou Jin

27:42.920 --> 27:43.920
and Qi Yan are.

27:44.640 --> 27:45.370
Think of a way

27:45.960 --> 27:47.510
to soothe Qi Yan's emotions.

27:47.510 --> 27:49.070
Just say yes to whatever conditions

27:49.070 --> 27:49.790
he makes

27:50.750 --> 27:51.720
to buy us time

27:51.880 --> 27:52.740
for the rescue.

27:53.900 --> 27:54.740
Don't worry.

27:55.820 --> 27:57.680
We won't take any reckless action

27:58.070 --> 27:59.930
until we're sure Zhou Jin is safe.

28:00.350 --> 28:01.070
You must...

28:02.470 --> 28:04.130
bring her home safe and sound.

28:05.680 --> 28:06.240
Got it.

28:15.270 --> 28:16.600
It all hinges on you now.

28:37.480 --> 28:38.280
Action Team 1,

28:38.880 --> 28:41.110
make sure Professor Jiang is safe.

28:41.680 --> 28:43.160
Stay well hidden,

28:43.160 --> 28:43.830
and try your best

28:43.830 --> 28:45.160
to keep him in sight.

28:45.960 --> 28:46.620
Roger that.

28:46.880 --> 28:50.200
Deputy head of the Provincial Bureau's
Criminal Investigation Department,

28:50.200 --> 28:51.440
Liu Zishan, has arrived on site.

28:51.440 --> 28:52.840
If any emergency arises,

28:53.010 --> 28:54.300
obey Commander Liu's orders

28:54.300 --> 28:55.830
as the highest directives.

29:14.390 --> 29:16.590
A surveillance camera at the entrance.

29:21.660 --> 29:22.420
Qi Yan!

29:23.790 --> 29:24.650
I'm already in.

29:26.070 --> 29:26.870
Where are you?

29:47.550 --> 29:48.960
Report to the command center:

29:48.960 --> 29:51.360
Professor Jiang is in observation point 1.

30:18.710 --> 30:19.230
Report:

30:19.920 --> 30:22.320
Professor Jiang is in observation point 2.

30:37.110 --> 30:38.000
Qi Yan!

30:41.800 --> 30:43.120
Report to the command center:

30:43.120 --> 30:45.450
Professor Jiang has entered a blind spot.

30:52.640 --> 30:53.240
Chief Tan,

30:53.660 --> 30:55.920
I found the stairway to the second floor.

30:57.350 --> 30:58.080
Action team,

30:58.270 --> 31:00.330
try keeping up with Professor Jiang.

31:05.140 --> 31:05.860
Report:

31:06.130 --> 31:08.130
One active camera on the outer wall.

31:10.030 --> 31:11.070
Stay alert

31:11.070 --> 31:12.870
in areas visible to the cameras,

31:13.330 --> 31:14.610
so Qi Yan can see you.

31:15.080 --> 31:16.880
But don't get into the building.

31:19.400 --> 31:20.240
Is there a way

31:20.790 --> 31:22.030
to breach from upstairs?

31:22.030 --> 31:23.090
All first-floor entries

31:23.090 --> 31:24.490
are under surveillance.

31:24.590 --> 31:25.770
I think we stand a higher chance

31:25.770 --> 31:27.430
of breaking in from upstairs.

31:27.750 --> 31:29.200
Then let our men do a free climb.

31:29.200 --> 31:29.750
Okay.

31:30.400 --> 31:31.570
Action Team 1,

31:31.960 --> 31:33.820
get ready to climb over the walls.

32:46.960 --> 32:48.890
Professor Jiang, what's going on?

33:04.520 --> 33:06.450
Professor Jiang, what's going on?

33:07.130 --> 33:08.130
Professor Jiang,

33:08.160 --> 33:09.090
this is Tan Shiming.

33:09.090 --> 33:10.570
Please respond if you copy.

33:10.570 --> 33:11.700
Chief Tan, I'm here.

33:12.350 --> 33:14.240
Surveillance cameras are everywhere
in the villa.

33:14.240 --> 33:15.880
I haven't found Zhou Jin's location yet.

33:15.880 --> 33:16.880
Professor Jiang,

33:17.350 --> 33:19.550
try to locate Qi Yan as soon as possible.

33:19.790 --> 33:21.120
Distract his attention

33:21.350 --> 33:22.950
from the surveillance feed.

33:23.680 --> 33:25.210
We'll find a way to break in.

33:25.260 --> 33:25.780
Got it.

33:30.100 --> 33:31.100
Professor Jiang,

33:31.930 --> 33:33.330
drop your gun

33:34.090 --> 33:35.890
and that walkie-talkie.

34:03.520 --> 34:04.360
Come up here.

34:05.460 --> 34:06.550
I'm waiting for you

34:06.890 --> 34:07.950
on the third floor.

35:02.000 --> 35:04.800
Your girl, Officer Zhou,
had me suffer quite a lot.

35:11.950 --> 35:12.950
Long time no see,

35:14.240 --> 35:15.100
Officer Jiang.

35:16.230 --> 35:16.800
No.

35:18.190 --> 35:19.360
I should call you

35:21.670 --> 35:23.000
"Professor Jiang" now.

35:24.320 --> 35:25.520
It's been a long time.

35:27.920 --> 35:29.650
Sit. Let's do some catching up.

35:52.220 --> 35:53.220
Where is Zhou Jin?

35:53.670 --> 35:54.670
Professor Jiang,

35:57.070 --> 35:58.950
when you beg others, act like it.

36:00.090 --> 36:01.450
Between us, there are still

36:01.450 --> 36:02.730
many unsolved issues.

36:03.550 --> 36:04.840
Officer Zhou's matter

36:06.010 --> 36:06.970
can wait.

36:15.950 --> 36:16.950
What do I have to do

36:17.630 --> 36:19.030
for you to let Zhou Jin go?

36:19.380 --> 36:20.310
All you need to do

36:21.800 --> 36:23.800
is answer two questions of mine.

36:25.190 --> 36:26.070
Then I will...

36:27.580 --> 36:28.980
consider releasing her.

36:29.030 --> 36:29.630
Ask away.

36:30.480 --> 36:32.010
Here is the first question.

36:32.590 --> 36:35.240
Years ago,
by the time you shot my brother dead,

36:37.670 --> 36:39.580
had he already surrendered?

36:42.810 --> 36:44.480
Answer my question.

36:49.450 --> 36:50.110
Yes, he had.

36:51.760 --> 36:52.320
Good.

36:54.150 --> 36:55.750
Here is the second question.

36:56.670 --> 36:59.000
Back then, to shield you from punishment,

36:59.040 --> 37:02.440
did Yao Weihai assert strongly
that you were not of sound mind

37:03.110 --> 37:04.370
when you fired the gun?

37:06.410 --> 37:07.160
Yes, he did.

37:07.710 --> 37:09.250
Very good.

37:10.630 --> 37:11.360
These two questions

37:11.360 --> 37:13.110
haunted me for a long time.

37:14.800 --> 37:16.730
Today, I finally have the answers.

37:22.350 --> 37:23.790
What would you have done

37:24.930 --> 37:26.050
if I had said no?

37:39.070 --> 37:40.470
Do you remember that bet?

37:41.280 --> 37:42.320
Do you remember

37:42.850 --> 37:44.310
the days in the warehouse?

37:45.150 --> 37:46.210
I miss them so much.

37:47.360 --> 37:48.890
Professor Jiang, how about

37:49.440 --> 37:50.900
doing one more bet with me?

37:52.070 --> 37:53.600
This time, the wager will be

37:56.390 --> 37:57.840
Officer Zhou's life.

37:58.180 --> 38:00.000
I don't like betting with human lives.

38:00.000 --> 38:01.330
I know you don't like it,

38:01.450 --> 38:02.700
but I do.

38:03.760 --> 38:04.760
Professor Jiang,

38:05.490 --> 38:06.490
your girl

38:07.220 --> 38:08.970
has put on a red dress.

38:09.960 --> 38:11.280
What a gorgeous lady.

38:13.840 --> 38:15.550
She's meant to be the wager.

38:16.580 --> 38:18.040
Come on, Professor Jiang.

38:18.630 --> 38:20.670
We're destined to have this bet.

38:21.020 --> 38:22.620
Play with me again, will you?

38:23.030 --> 38:23.760
I swear,

38:24.280 --> 38:25.760
this time, if you win,

38:26.280 --> 38:28.410
I'll let Officer Zhou go immediately.

38:29.830 --> 38:30.830
What do you think?

38:33.360 --> 38:34.160
Come on.

38:35.710 --> 38:37.370
Just play with me again, okay?

38:38.590 --> 38:40.280
Please, Professor Jiang.

38:41.800 --> 38:42.880
Jiang Hansheng!

38:43.670 --> 38:45.510
Grab your gun!

38:47.410 --> 38:48.050
Qi Yan,

38:49.510 --> 38:50.630
if you want to play,

38:51.400 --> 38:53.000
I'll play along till the end.

38:53.920 --> 38:56.380
But before that,
I need to ask a question too.

38:56.570 --> 38:58.230
Only you have the answer to it.

39:02.070 --> 39:03.550
The knowledgeable Professor Jiang

39:03.550 --> 39:05.810
actually has a question he can't answer.

39:10.230 --> 39:11.280
Why did Wen Lang insist on

39:11.280 --> 39:13.480
handing over the photos to me years ago?

39:14.360 --> 39:16.820
Only you knew
the consequences of this move.

39:17.400 --> 39:19.460
You wanted me to kill him, didn't you?

39:27.360 --> 39:28.360
Professor Jiang,

39:29.550 --> 39:30.670
this is no good.

39:31.620 --> 39:33.480
That sounds like a sinister plan.

39:33.690 --> 39:35.090
It was you who killed him.

39:35.640 --> 39:37.290
What? After all these years,

39:38.400 --> 39:40.100
you're shifting the blame to me now?

39:40.100 --> 39:40.960
You hypocrite.

39:41.920 --> 39:43.650
You not only refuse to thank me,

39:43.710 --> 39:46.240
but also act like
you're taking revenge on me.

39:48.550 --> 39:49.670
A flaw has emerged.

39:50.150 --> 39:51.030
So, Professor Jiang,

39:51.030 --> 39:53.050
do you admit that you were of sound mind

39:53.050 --> 39:55.010
when you pulled the trigger?

39:55.040 --> 39:56.440
Yes, I was clear-headed.

39:57.230 --> 39:59.290
I knew the person I had to kill was you.

39:59.440 --> 40:00.900
But what about you, Qi Yan?

40:01.190 --> 40:02.850
You've killed so many people.

40:03.030 --> 40:04.430
Who did you kill them for?

40:04.920 --> 40:06.520
You showed tons of giveaways

40:06.560 --> 40:08.030
through your habits in crimes.

40:08.030 --> 40:09.560
Every substitute you chose

40:09.750 --> 40:12.390
reveals your incompetence and cowardice.

40:13.030 --> 40:14.710
A person is weighing on your heart,

40:14.710 --> 40:16.840
yet you dare not lay a hand on him or her.

40:16.950 --> 40:18.010
Who is this person?

40:20.920 --> 40:22.960
Don't act like you know me well.

40:27.470 --> 40:28.720
I know who that is.

40:28.740 --> 40:30.060
Shut up.

40:30.080 --> 40:31.740
In fact, I'm luckier than you.

40:32.960 --> 40:34.090
The person I love...

40:34.810 --> 40:35.960
loves me too.

40:50.760 --> 40:51.820
Proud, aren't you?

40:56.360 --> 40:57.820
Zhou Jin is not with Qi Yan.

40:57.880 --> 41:00.150
Jiang Hansheng is trying
to get information out of him.

41:00.150 --> 41:00.960
Jiang Cheng?

41:01.760 --> 41:02.890
Why are you in there?

41:06.230 --> 41:07.490
Report your location.

41:09.670 --> 41:10.410
The third floor.

41:10.410 --> 41:11.810
We are on the third floor.

41:11.960 --> 41:13.490
Zhou Jin is in grave danger.

41:14.400 --> 41:15.960
The hostage is not with the suspect.

41:15.960 --> 41:17.220
This is not a good sign.

41:17.410 --> 41:20.210
We must quickly confirm
if Zhou Jin is still alive.

41:20.440 --> 41:20.880
Yes.

41:22.480 --> 41:23.360
In this case,

41:24.710 --> 41:26.310
I might as well reciprocate.

41:28.150 --> 41:29.550
Let's talk about Qi Zhen.

41:31.800 --> 41:32.960
What about her?

41:35.030 --> 41:37.160
She said she doesn't hate you anymore,

41:37.400 --> 41:39.600
despite everything you did in the past.

41:46.360 --> 41:48.190
Jiang Hansheng is provoking Qi Yan.

41:48.190 --> 41:49.800
He's probably trying to make him
empty his magazine.

41:49.800 --> 41:50.860
No action until you hear gun shots.

41:50.860 --> 41:51.520
Roger that.

41:52.920 --> 41:54.230
Why would she say that?

41:54.550 --> 41:55.840
Because she is done

41:56.550 --> 41:58.750
hating people and things from the past.

42:00.070 --> 42:01.320
What does that mean?

42:03.550 --> 42:04.550
She and Jian Liang

42:05.230 --> 42:06.680
have their own child now,

42:07.590 --> 42:09.430
a child growing up in happiness.

42:24.920 --> 42:26.070
I don't believe it.

42:30.590 --> 42:32.150
I don't believe it.

42:32.750 --> 42:33.920
Jiang Hansheng,

42:34.670 --> 42:36.070
you're lying to me.

42:36.920 --> 42:39.760
You're lying to me!

42:48.510 --> 42:49.710
Breach immediately!

42:58.400 --> 42:59.280
Leave this to me.

42:59.280 --> 43:00.410
You go find Zhou Jin.

43:00.710 --> 43:01.280
Be careful.
